name: Game 1/52, Game A Week Challenge. "I cant program"
name_original: Game 1/52, Game A Week Challenge. "I cant program"
description: This is the 1st game I have made in a week, part of the GaW challenge. This game is super simple, super ugly, and I am happy to have made it, since I am not a programmer. Wasd to move, collect the default unity sprite stopwatches to win, and blue circles kill you. Enjoy!
